'From Squeak2.9alpha of 17 July 2000 [latest update: #2938] on 2 November 2000 at 1:34:47 pm'!"Change Set:		whosOnFirstDate:			2 November 2000Author:			Bob Arning- fix to make it easier to add other morphs as submorphs of EmbeddedWorldBorderMorph"!!EmbeddedWorldBorderMorph methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'RAA 11/2/2000 13:31'!fixLayout	submorphs size < 1 ifTrue: [^super fixLayout].	self myTransformation bounds: self innerBounds.! !!EmbeddedWorldBorderMorph methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'RAA 11/2/2000 13:31'!myTransformation	^submorphs detect: [ :x | x isKindOf: TransformationMorph] ifNone: [nil]! !!EmbeddedWorldBorderMorph methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'RAA 11/2/2000 13:31'!myWorldChanged	self layoutChanged.	submorphs isEmpty ifFalse: [		self myTransformation extentFromParent: self innerBounds extent.		bounds _ bounds topLeft extent: self myTransformation extent + (borderWidth * 2).	].	self changed.! !!EmbeddedWorldBorderMorph methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'RAA 11/2/2000 13:31'!worldIEnclose	^self myTransformation firstSubmorph						"quick hack since this is the only usage pattern at the moment"! !